{"tid":1112840,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中國聯想推出配備100,000,000像素相機嘅機皇，吊打華為三星蘋果，稱霸手機界","createTime":"2019-04-17T15:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T13:28:44.000Z","uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"40dd07f1dc301e4a87dc373368b108d9fcd23ec7","tid":1112840,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"Lenovo 集團副總裁常程在微博中發言，在本月，擁有<strong>一億像素</strong>的機皇&mdash;&mdash; <strong>Lenovo Z6 Pro</strong> 將會在本月於北京與我們見面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/423422442323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F423422442323.jpg&h=f1e3418d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在公佈的的官方的宣傳圖中看出 Lenovo Z6 Pro 將設有億級像素主相機，可以拍攝 <strong>1億像素</strong>相片，並且擁有神秘的 Hyper Video 功能。由此可見 Lenovo Z6 Pro 是款主打拍攝的旗艦手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/42342222442323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F42342222442323.jpg&h=0b6b9f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLenovo Z6 Pro 會不會真正配置 1億萬像素感光元件，或者是通過插植達成拍攝 1億萬像素相片？這還需要不久之後的正式發布來證實。"},{"pid":"bef475a66fee35cc4e703aee8fdeb038ded5a617","tid":1112840,"uid":196924,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"幾年前出就有用<br />\n而家連師奶阿嬸都知唔係像素高就等於靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15af48a4120af514cc07d81d50a0937677b9e88","tid":1112840,"uid":20368,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"bef475a66fee35cc4e703aee8fdeb038ded5a617","tid":1112840,"uid":196924,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"幾年前出就有用<br />\n而家連師奶阿嬸都知唔係像素高就等於靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"雖然話高像素唔代表靚<br />\n但佢拉到1億，斷估都唔會好差掛<br />\n有5成都已經靚過大部份相機"},{"pid":